<plot>Hungry For Your Love is the story of a teen rocker who falls asleep in the first class cabin of an airliner, while being heckled by the passenger behind him. While asleep, Cardenas dreams about the stunningly beautiful stewardess morphing into a tiger, that chases him through the streets of Los Angeles. When the airplane lands, the passengers and stewardess are in for a huge surprise.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?250348</url></doc>
